239
00:14:51,808 --> 00:14:54,769
Gosto mais de jazz,
mas toda a música é boa.

240
00:14:54,852 --> 00:14:56,270
Ajuda a aguentar o dia.

241
00:14:58,064 --> 00:14:58,898
Toma.

242
00:15:01,025 --> 00:15:04,320
