de falar contigo um dia destes

243
00:15:04,404 --> 00:15:05,405
sobre a Hannah Baker.

244
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:10,785
A Hannah? Porquê?

245
00:15:10,868 --> 00:15:13,079
