Eu sou completamente Aquela Rapariga.

294
00:17:05,650 --> 00:17:07,068
Eu sou Aquela Outra Rapariga.

295
00:17:11,489 --> 00:17:13,574
A estúpida da Sra. Antilly.

296
00:17:14,158 --> 00:17:15,701
